text: Mok Un-ju (born 29 March 1981) is a North Korean gymnast. She competed in five events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:North Korean female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of North Korea Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Gymnasts at the 1998 Asian Games
